cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with the task of saliency detection in light field images using deep convolutional networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the modeling of angular patterns, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR). The use of deep learning techniques for image processing and analysis can also be categorized under multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
